Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.71,0:00:04.42,Default,,0,0,0,,And now, it's your morning horoscope countdown!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.58,0:00:09.25,Default,,0,0,0,,In the top spot, it's YOU, Pisces! We predict you'll\Nbe getting close to a certain special someone!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.17,0:01:49.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Umaruuuun!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.58,0:01:51.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Kirie, we're at the amusement park!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.79,0:01:53.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes we are, Umaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.92,0:02:05.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Kirie?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.25,0:02:07.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Kirie!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.25,0:02:09.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.71,0:02:11.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you feel bad?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.25,0:02:13.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, i-it's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.25,0:02:17.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't been to an amusement park in a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.79,0:02:20.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Indeed, I'm looking forward to us all going together!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.29,0:02:23.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.75,0:02:25.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry to keep you waiting!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.83,0:02:27.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Umaru...!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.67,0:02:31.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay, Kirie?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.50,0:02:41.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Your shoelaces were untied. That's dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.75,0:02:45.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just glad you didn't get hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.33,0:02:48.17,Default,,0,0,0,,This is my first time to ride a bus, indeed!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.17,0:02:50.92,Default,,0,0,0,,We should get to Fujiyama Land in no time!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.13,0:02:57.58,Default,,0,0,0,,No! You mustn't push that button!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.83,0:02:59.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.33,0:03:09.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Fujiyama Land has a lot of rides, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.33,0:03:11.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! I brought a pamphlet with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.92,0:03:16.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Indeed, I want to ride the roller coaster!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.75,0:03:19.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the longest in the world! It's the best, indeed!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.50,0:03:23.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I want to ride the merry-go-round.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.79,0:03:25.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't been on one since I was a child...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.79,0:03:29.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to ride the spinning teacups.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.50,0:03:32.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to try this "Hardcore Piloting Experience."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.63,0:03:35.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You damn monsters! Die, die!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.33,0:03:43.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! It looks like we're here!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.79,0:03:44.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Squee!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.96,0:03:54.13,Default,,0,0,0,,We've reached the front gate, indeed!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.00,0:03:57.92,Default,,0,0,0,,This is indeed where they sell tickets!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.92,0:04:00.79,Default,,0,0,0,,With a "free pass," you can ride anything you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.50,0:04:06.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no! My eyes were closed!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.54,0:04:09.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry. You're still cute, Sylphin.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.46,0:04:11.79,Default,,0,0,0,,You look so pretty in yours, Umaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.79,0:04:13.63,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I really don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.71,0:04:21.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! They're doing an anime song concert!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.71,0:04:25.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Amusement parks even have events like THIS, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.42,0:04:27.29,Default,,0,0,0,,U-um...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.29,0:04:27.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.92,0:04:30.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to use the bathroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.46,0:04:31.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.42,0:04:38.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I think this horoscope is a lie...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.00,0:04:42.50,Default,,0,0,0,,This is bad! I've been gone too long!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.50,0:04:50.13,Default,,0,0,0,,No, NO! I can't make Umaru\Nworry more than I already have!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.13,0:04:53.17,Default,,0,0,0,,She might never invite me to anything again!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.88,0:04:58.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Umaru...?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.25,0:05:00.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's Cold and Bristly Girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.67,0:05:02.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You came to the anime concert as well, did you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.88,0:05:10.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.63,0:05:13.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Big Brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.04,0:05:16.92,Default,,0,0,0,,"Brother"?! True, they're pretty similar!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.29,0:05:19.67,Default,,0,0,0,,She had the same reaction as me...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.58,0:05:22.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you a friend of Sylphin's?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.21,0:05:23.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Shpaa!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.21,0:05:24.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm her brother, Alex.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.83,0:05:29.71,Default,,0,0,0,,This is some merchandise I got at the anime event.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.71,0:05:30.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.92,0:05:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.21,0:05:38.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Sylphin, the show's over, so I'll be going now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.71,0:05:40.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Big Brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.96,0:05:42.83,Default,,0,0,0,,He's quite thoughtful, isn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.96,0:05:44.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.79,0:05:48.67,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, Kirie, had you met him before?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.25,0:05:51.88,Default,,0,0,0,,No! Not at all! I don't know him!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.08,0:05:57.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Your brother, you say? Eheheheh...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.13,0:05:59.29,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no laughter at all in those eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.88,0:06:02.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, what do you say we ride something?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.46,0:06:04.21,Default,,0,0,0,,A-a good idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.38,0:06:06.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Why, yes! Let's have fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.75,0:06:11.42,Default,,0,0,0,,This is fast, indeed!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.38,0:06:19.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I am... stumbling... indeed...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.79,0:06:22.17,Default,,0,0,0,,That was meant for kids,\Nso the seats were a little crowded, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.25,0:06:24.17,Default,,0,0,0,,But it was really fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.33,0:06:25.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I could've used an airbag...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.50,0:06:27.04,Default,,0,0,0,,What should we ride next?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.00,0:06:32.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to invite Umaru\Nto ride a spinning teacup with me...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.63,0:06:33.88,Default,,0,0,0,,What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.08,0:06:42.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.04,0:06:44.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Indeed, I wish to ride THAT!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.25,0:06:54.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I'm not scared...!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.79,0:06:58.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll be fine. Indeed, it's almost our turn in line!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.17,0:06:59.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.00,0:06:59.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Say...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.46,0:07:02.17,Default,,0,0,0,,how tall are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.00,0:07:05.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't ride if you're less than 140 cm tall.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.46,0:07:11.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a shame, indeed. We were in line for an hour...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.00,0:07:14.46,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nothing we can do about it now.\NLet's ride something else.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.58,0:07:18.46,Default,,0,0,0,,That horoscope was completely wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.71,0:07:20.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Today has been nothing but bad luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.04,0:07:25.88,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn't just about me, though. I don't want\Nto inconvenience the others, so I'll just keep quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.08,0:07:41.25,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.54,0:07:42.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.67,0:07:43.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Your hair!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.33,0:07:54.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Kirie, let's ride the Ferris Wheel.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.13,0:08:02.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.04,0:08:07.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Good thing you could use Alex's present\Nas a hair fastener, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.25,0:08:13.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I-it's just me and Umaru, alone together.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.71,0:08:16.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to say something.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.21,0:08:19.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Something... something!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.21,0:08:21.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Um...!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.04,0:08:27.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It's pretty boring, isn't it? Hanging out with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.92,0:08:33.63,Default,,0,0,0,,We wasted an hour in line\Nfor the roller coaster because of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.08,0:08:37.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, I worried everyone by crying out loud...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.00,0:08:40.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Why am I saying this?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.83,0:08:45.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't even take a decent photo\Nfor my free pass. I'm basically cursed.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.25,0:08:51.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm such an idiot. This is all I can talk about... THIS?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.00,0:08:57.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Jeez... there's no way\Nshe'll want to hang out with me again.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.67,0:09:03.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Nah...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.33,0:09:08.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been a LOT of fun, Kirie!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.00,0:09:11.42,Default,,0,0,0,,M-me too!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.75,0:09:14.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I've had lots of...!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.04,0:09:15.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.67,0:09:18.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You know what?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.54,0:09:21.96,Default,,0,0,0,,We haven't gone on THAT yet, have we?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.29,0:09:28.58,Default,,0,0,0,,The teacups!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.88,0:09:34.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.58,0:09:49.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Jeez...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.88,0:09:53.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Indeed!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.00,0:09:57.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.42,0:10:00.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You're getting an award in front of the whole school?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.42,0:10:04.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah... it's a friggin' pain...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.83,0:10:07.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You wouldn't think THIS person would get an award...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.96,0:10:10.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone will be rooting for you, so don't flake out.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.04,0:10:14.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't even really care about it...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.71,0:10:16.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Umaruuun!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.17,0:10:18.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Umaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.83,0:10:21.71,Default,,0,0,0,,She'll be getting an award today\Nfor having the highest GPA!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.96,0:10:23.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.04,0:10:26.21,Default,,0,0,0,,C-congratulations!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.75,0:10:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.13,0:10:30.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Shbaa!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.42,0:10:32.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Congratulations to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.13,0:10:34.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Sylphin...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.79,0:10:37.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm? What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.92,0:10:39.33,Default,,0,0,0,,W-well...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.71,0:10:43.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You shall not beat me on these upcoming midterms!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.00,0:10:44.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Shbafeen!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.67,0:10:45.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I, Sylphinford Tachibana, will take first place!\NShbafeen!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.46,0:10:48.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I, Sylphinford Tachibana, will take first place!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.54,0:10:51.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You've thought of Umaru as your rival, haven't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.33,0:10:54.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you really wish her well?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.21,0:11:03.67,Default,,0,0,0,,C-come to think of it, before I started hanging out\Nwith you all, I DID think of Umaru as my rival...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.13,0:11:08.50,Default,,0,0,0,,But now, I'm as happy for her as if it were myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.08,0:11:15.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Indeed, is this strange?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.42,0:11:18.13,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's not.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.13,0:11:20.13,Default,,0,0,0,,It's up until now that you've been strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.67,0:11:24.25,Default,,0,0,0,,The award ceremony will soon commence.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.83,0:11:29.04,Default,,0,0,0,,For academic excellence\Nin general coursework: Umaru Doma.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.38,0:11:32.71,Default,,0,0,0,,My friends are all supporting me...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.67,0:11:35.25,Default,,0,0,0,,They're all happy for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.08,0:11:37.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.79,0:11:44.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Umaru, you are cool indeed!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.92,0:11:51.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Next up, the award for academic excellence\Nin AP courses goes to...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.92,0:11:58.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Hikari Kongo.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.29,0:12:11.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.42,0:12:19.38,Default,,0,0,0,,That was a splendid awards ceremony!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.83,0:12:21.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.83,0:12:24.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Still...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.08,0:12:30.46,Default,,0,0,0,,That was the first time I've seen someone\Nfrom the AP classes. They're in a separate building, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.79,0:12:33.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-yes, you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.46,0:12:36.17,Default,,0,0,0,,AP classes...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.96,0:12:42.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Your grades are beyond reproach,\NUmaru. They're exemplary.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.71,0:12:47.79,Default,,0,0,0,,If you like, we could move you into the AP curriculum...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.58,0:12:55.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Have I met that girl somewhere before?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.92,0:13:07.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Cassiopeia... Altair...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.08,0:13:09.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Deneb...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.92,0:13:14.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Arcturus... Spica.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.33,0:13:26.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I finally get it...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.58,0:13:30.58,Default,,0,0,0,,This whole time, what I've searched for\Nhas been right in front of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.33,0:13:32.83,Default,,0,0,0,,This light...!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.21,0:13:35.79,Default,,0,0,0,,It can't be... The fifth Precura!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.42,0:13:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,The light of justice: Cura Big-Bang!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.63,0:13:45.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, everyone. I... I have no more doubts!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.50,0:13:54.17,Default,,0,0,0,,That was wonderful, wasn't it, Sensei? What a climax!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.17,0:13:56.67,Default,,0,0,0,,The scene where Big-Bang\Nbecame part of the group, right!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.08,0:14:02.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Big-Bang was a loner at first, but in the end,\Nshe had the courage to make friends with the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.08,0:14:07.67,Default,,0,0,0,,That long process made\Nthe climax so much more powerful!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.25,0:14:08.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Shba!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.96,0:14:11.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Wasn't it great, Cold and Bristly Girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.17,0:14:12.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.29,0:14:15.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't trust this guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.25,0:14:18.71,Default,,0,0,0,,He calls my master "Sensei." Just what is he plotting?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.38,0:14:21.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I am the Master's one and only disciple!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.79,0:14:23.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I must protect her!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.13,0:14:28.42,Default,,0,0,0,,So, Alex, do you go back to Germany\Nwhen you want to see your friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.42,0:14:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh... um... Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.04,0:14:34.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm ashamed to admit it, but when I was in Germany...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.88,0:14:38.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I wasn't like Big-Bang, but I was pretty withdrawn.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.33,0:14:39.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.63,0:14:42.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, in middle school...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.92,0:14:45.46,Default,,0,0,0,,One day, I couldn't bring myself to go to school.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.13,0:14:49.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I spent my days online or watching anime.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.38,0:14:55.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Once you've locked yourself indoors,\Nit's hard to go back outside, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.79,0:15:00.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I convinced myself I didn't need to interact\Nwith others in order to live.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.38,0:15:04.33,Default,,0,0,0,,But then...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.83,0:15:06.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Suddenly, the day came!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.79,0:15:13.04,Default,,0,0,0,,My savior arrived, the one who suggested\NI go to high school in Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.13,0:15:18.25,Default,,0,0,0,,That was when my life changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.58,0:15:23.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You've both been so kind to me\Nsince I joined the company...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.75,0:15:28.21,Default,,0,0,0,,And thanks to you, I got to meet Sensei\Nand even Cold and Bristly Girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.71,0:15:34.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I get it now; Everyday life means people helping people.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.00,0:15:38.67,Default,,0,0,0,,The light of justice: Cura Big-Bang!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.83,0:15:40.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.08,0:15:42.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-wha-?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.08,0:15:50.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, what's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.54,0:15:52.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, nothing. Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.71,0:15:56.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Say, let's come up with some sweet poses\Nfor those key scenes!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.17,0:15:59.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Sounds great! Let's do it, Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.25,0:16:06.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll do it too!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.54,0:16:10.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Even Cold and Bristly Girl is getting in on it, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.71,0:16:12.67,Default,,0,0,0,,D-don't go getting the wrong idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.04,0:16:18.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I am the Master's top pupil! This is why\NI participate in what SHE wants to do!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.54,0:16:20.71,Default,,0,0,0,,So, let's all do it together!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.54,0:16:23.79,Default,,0,0,0,,The light of justice: Cura Big-Bang!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.13,0:16:26.92,Default,,0,0,0,,The light of justice: Cura Big-Bang!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.17,0:16:30.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, Sensei. See you next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.13,0:16:32.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Till then, Alex!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.25,0:16:41.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.54,0:16:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a savior...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.83,0:16:51.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.04,0:16:53.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Kanau!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.04,0:16:56.08,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing here?\NI told you everything on the phone!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.29,0:17:01.08,Default,,0,0,0,,How can you say that?\NWe have to celebrate Hikari's award!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.58,0:17:06.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Here! Let's mark the occasion\Nby watching the Precura Blu-ray box set!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.08,0:17:14.79,Default,,0,0,0,,No thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.96,0:17:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,WHY NOT?! The final scene where Big-Bang\Nbecome part of the group is fantastic!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.00,0:17:20.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't care.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.88,0:17:22.21,Default,,0,0,0,,WHAAAAAAAAT?!\NThis guy hasn't changed at all since middle school.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.21,0:17:23.96,Default,,0,0,0,,This guy hasn't changed at all since middle school.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.79,0:17:27.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.63,0:17:32.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Kanau! Sen... I mean, Umaru and I\Nwatched some anime again today!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.92,0:17:34.71,Default,,0,0,0,,And Taihei wasn't there!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.71,0:17:38.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I don't need every little detail, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.75,0:17:48.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so hot.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.29,0:17:54.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd sure like some chilled rice soup...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.29,0:18:01.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Rolling around with my pretty kitty, Necolumbus...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.88,0:18:04.54,Default,,0,0,0,,My best dish is...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.88,0:18:07.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.50,0:18:18.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Reckon I passed out. My head's all fuzzy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.29,0:18:24.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm scared. Maybe I'm fixin' to up and die!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.92,0:18:32.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Nana.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.63,0:18:36.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I made you some chilled rice soup.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.04,0:18:38.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Big Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.88,0:18:43.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.88,0:18:46.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Am I gonna die?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.08,0:18:50.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Ain't no way that'll happen. It's just a heatstroke.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.83,0:18:53.42,Default,,0,0,0,,And you ain't eaten, so your body's all weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.04,0:18:55.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Eat up now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.33,0:19:07.21,Default,,0,0,0,,That sure is great!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.21,0:19:10.88,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the last memory I have of my brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.58,0:19:16.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Big Brother! I ate it and I'm all better now!\NCan you teach me how to make...?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.88,0:19:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.75,0:19:23.13,Default,,0,0,0,,My brother was gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.29,0:19:28.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Your brother had to go and get a job.\NReckon he'll be back soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.79,0:19:33.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I still didn't understand why he left, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.25,0:19:36.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew where he went.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.50,0:19:41.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Nana, that restaurant we went to\Nin Tokyo was great, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.46,0:19:44.08,Default,,0,0,0,,One day, I'm gonna live in Tokyo too!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.00,0:19:47.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't see as how it's a big deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.42,0:19:50.46,Default,,0,0,0,,We've all been to Tokyo before.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.88,0:19:53.33,Default,,0,0,0,,But you ain't never been there alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.67,0:19:56.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Plus, visitin' somewhere don't mean you can LIVE there.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.63,0:20:01.33,Default,,0,0,0,,But, Tokyo's too far for me\Nto go to school there and live here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.25,0:20:20.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.46,0:20:24.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.75,0:20:30.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! I-I'm sorry! I-I-I just moved here today!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.67,0:20:33.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.50,0:20:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-this man...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.83,0:20:39.33,Default,,0,0,0,,He sort of reminds me of my brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.67,0:20:45.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd spoken to Umaru's brother a few times, and maybe....
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.13,0:20:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,maybe I've sort of thought of him as MY brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.71,0:21:11.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Ebina...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.42,0:21:13.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.46,0:21:14.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You're really kind, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.21,0:21:21.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Ebina.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.83,0:21:23.58,Default,,0,0,0,,G-good afternoon!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.58,0:21:28.29,Default,,0,0,0,,It's hot today, so if you stay outside too long,\Nyou'll get a heatstroke.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.63,0:21:30.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-y-yes, you're right!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.00,0:21:41.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like that time before, when my head was all fuzzy...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.38,0:21:54.13,Default,,0,0,0,,But somehow, it's not scary. It's a happy kind of fuzzy.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.67,0:23:28.67,Default,,0,0,0,,That amusement park was fun indeed!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.79,0:23:30.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Yup! I'd like to go again.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.50,0:23:34.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Kirie seemed a little off-put at first,\Nbut by the end, she was indeed enjoying herself!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.71,0:23:36.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You're so thoughtful, Sylphin.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.75,0:23:40.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not sure I follow, but I shall accept that compliment!
